name: Synth sETH
description: Experimental ERC20 token for academic research. Not for investment. Differences with the official sETH are explained on the website and social media.
extended_description: This token is created to study user behavior and network interactions in DeFi. Official sETH is migrating with low trading activity, allowing this token to be used for research purposes only. Liquidity is provided, holders exceed 12,000, and transactions exceed 15,500.
